Class Room

java.lang.Object
spring2024.cs472.hotelwebsite.entities.Room
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
@Entity public class Room extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a room in the hotel. This class contains attributes such as room number, room type, price, floor number, and occupancy status.
